_header: Hector that was of all knights flower

BLHar2259.First Lines:
Ector þat was all knyghtes flowerWhich euer gate hym with his
                    hond honour…
BLHar2259.Last Lines:
…But crowne of gold non weryd þat conquerorBecause
                    þat crownyd with thorn was his saueor
